review_desc: I visited Sandwich Corner last week and was blown away by the quality of their sandwiches. The bread was perfectly toasted, and the balance of meats and veggies was spot on. Definitely coming back for more!
The portions are generous, and the service is quick. A must-visit spot for sandwich lovers!

I was really looking forward to trying Sandwich Corner due to all the rave reviews. However, my experience was marred by slow service. The sandwich I ordered was delicious, no doubt, but waiting over 30 minutes for a sandwich when the place wasn't even that busy was a letdown.

Happy and Healthy lives up to its name! My order was a delightful blend of fresh vegetables, perfectly cooked quinoa, and a flavorful dressing. This restaurant is a haven for health-conscious foodies. Definitely my go-to spot for a nutritious meal.

I had high expectations for Happy and Healthy based on its name and concept, but my experience fell short. The ambiance of the restaurant is pleasant, but that does not compensate for the lackluster meal and the hit to my wallet.
